"v.教导；灌输思想 【英】 v.教导; 灌输思想(to imbue with doctrines) 【考】 stickler : exact / pedagogue : indoctrinate(吹毛求疵者特点是苛 刻的/学究特点是教导) 【记】 in(进入)+doctrin(教 条，思想)+ate→使思 想进入→灌输 v. (以教条的方式来)教授, 教导 = imbue; 向...灌输(思想) 【记】in里面, doctrine(n 教条; 学说)－使教条进入你的头脑里面－灌输 【类】stickler: exact = pedagogue: indoctrinate吹毛求疵者擅长苛求 = 学究擅长教导 【记】in 进入 + doctrine 教条, 学说 + ate 动词→灌输进学说 indoctrinate (v.)  1620s, ""to teach,"" from in- (2) ""in"" + Latin doctrina ""teaching"" (see doctrine). Meaning ""to imbue with an idea or opinion"" first recorded 1832. Related: Indoctrinated; indoctrinating. The earlier verb was indoctrine (c.1500)."
